{"tid":936063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【華為二公主】哈佛電腦系高材生 高調現身巴黎名媛舞會引發揣測","createTime":"2018-12-10T13:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T13:36:00.000Z","uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9cff26314189a35322dc17a30bb6b007912c0224","tid":936063,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:14:37.000Z","msg":"華為公主孟晚舟被捕的消息，在全球股市引發震盪，但就在這個消息傳出的前幾天，華為的二公主Annabel Yao卻正在巴黎的名媛舞會中高調現身，甚至有媒體推測此舉是在為接班鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n「我當然是把這一場視為登上世界舞台的見面會。從現在開始，我就不再是活在自己世界裡的小女孩，而是踏入成人的世界，必須留意自己的舉止，讓外界檢視我的一舉一動，」姚安娜（Annabel Yao）在接受香港南華早報訪問時說。<br />\n<br />\n根據網路資料，現年21歲的Annabel Yao是華為創辦人任正非與第二任妻子姚玲所生的女兒，出生於雲南省昆明市。而日前被加拿大警方逮捕的孟晚舟，則是任正非與第一任妻子孟軍生下的女兒。從2個女兒的姓氏來看，任正非的兒女似乎都從母姓，而過去這位年輕二公主的行事也很低調，外界對她了解非常有限。<br />\n<br />\n正因為如此，Annabel Yao今年感恩節週末在巴黎社交場合的高調現身，就似乎顯得別有意涵。法國的「巴黎名媛舞會」是依循歐美「成年禮」傳統，讓年輕女孩正式踏入社交圈的大型晚會，但並非任何人想參加就可以參加，而是僅針對名門閨秀和名人子女提出邀請，每年甄選20位左右外貌出眾，或聰穎過人，或是有特殊背景的年輕女性，參加這場奢華派對。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/guikAM9QZNUUgjubcihWhw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/mirrormedia.mg/d217790c200f36fe82edea6f053eb431\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FguikAM9QZNUUgjubcihWhw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2Fd217790c200f36fe82edea6f053eb431&h=3e0cee4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在 Instagram 查看這則貼文<br />\n<br />\nI do not look like me in this but I don&rsquo;t hate being an emoji&zwj;♀️<br />\n<br />\nAnnabel Yao（@annabelballerina）分享的貼文 於 PST 2018 年 11月 月 29 日 上午 10:25 張貼<br />\n<img src=\"http://new-img1.bazaar.net.cn/bazaar/137/373/lipKqfMypalR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnew-img1.bazaar.net.cn%2Fbazaar%2F137%2F373%2FlipKqfMypalR.jpg&h=fa60cc63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據法國媒體對晚會的報導，今年舞會上的女孩，除了Annabel之外，還有AT&amp;T創辦人的女兒Julia McCaw、奧斯卡影帝Forest Whitaker的愛女，以及德國貴族之後等。但引人注意的是在舞會這段期間，Annabel連續登上了《Vogue》、《浮華世界》等雜誌版面，還有媒體以6版大篇幅報導Annabel的家世背景，刻意的高調，讓外界懷疑任正非或華為方面是否幕後有所安排。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/yao_pqcGY_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fyao_pqcGY_1200x0.png&h=19df668e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比利時伯爵 Gaspard de Limburg Stirum<br />\n<br />\n根據各方蒐集的資料，Annabel目前是哈佛大學電腦工程系大三學生，<span style=\"color: red;\">曾經居住在香港、英國牛津和上海。而從她的社群網站上，可以看到她拿著名牌包包、身穿名牌服飾在世界各地旅遊的身影。</span>她同時也是哈佛芭蕾舞團的成員，從5歲就開始學跳芭蕾舞；而在被問到日後的抱負時，Annabel對南華早報的記者表示她雖然是唸電腦的，卻對時尚、公關與娛樂事業很有興趣，未來可能會朝向科技產業的管理面，或經營領域發展。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BqtNSZwArad/?utm_source=ig_embed\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBqtNSZwArad%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed&h=6ebd666e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cbd6e16707d4e380fded016758c194fd4f24ed5","tid":936063,"uid":531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:17:38.000Z","msg":"佢有幾多本護照？"},{"pid":"e0af29bda0fd71b47ab90c3171a4f46fe3bb3b5f","tid":936063,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:24:13.000Z","msg":"呢條女閪窿屎眼早就俾洋腸塞到爆裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8ec1e789e77f3900ae0a57b55ef1c75c726d2c","tid":936063,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"無論點着都係成陣鄉下出嚟嘅支那味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e502f64d0c237b699c5992ed55a3b566280e28","tid":936063,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:26:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支那雞<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"068a6e7c8c19d3e303c68add4146901fcfc9542e","tid":936063,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:27:32.000Z","msg":"佢哋一個家族有幾多個姓㗎？"},{"pid":"204a6a46d6bb616793274758a4fb9372f2a60101","tid":936063,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:28:48.000Z","msg":"支那雞不了"},{"pid":"2748befe4c60402e8f3c87a808e78331a9be3ca6","tid":936063,"uid":59536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"068a6e7c8c19d3e303c68add4146901fcfc9542e","tid":936063,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:27:32.000Z","msg":"佢哋一個家族有幾多個姓㗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T13:36:00.000Z","msg":"跟母姓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}